SQL_STMT_U.val: select PAIN_RUNNUMBER, min(PAIN_BANK_ADMNO), min(PAIN_FILE_LEDG_NO), min(PAIN_BANKFILETYPE), min(PAIN_SPLIT_URGENT), min(PAIN_HGRP_CODE), min(PAIN_CURRENCY), min(ADMN_NAME), min(BANK_NAME), COUNT(*) as COUNT, cast(sum(PAIN_AMOUNT) as decimal (13,2)), min(PAIN_SHA1CHECKSUM) from :1/PAIN left outer join :1/ADMN on ADMN_NO = PAIN_BANK_ADMNO left outer join :1/BANK on BANK_ADMNO = PAIN_BANK_ADMNO and BANK_LEDG_NO = PAIN_FILE_LEDG_NO where PAIN_TRANSFERRED = 'Y' and PAIN_PAYMENTDATE = ':2' and exists (select * from :1/ADMU where ADMU_ADMNO = PAIN_ADMNO_DEBTOR and ADMU_HUSR_ID = ':3' and ADMU_ALLOW_CREATE_BANKFILES = 'Y') group by PAIN_RUNNUMBER order by PAIN_RUNNUMBER for fetch only
